  <thing id="fSetUp" name="Set-Up" description="When you score the perfect blow, you use it to set up a target for your next strike.\n\n{b}Prerequisite:{/b} Int 13, Combat Expertise, Improved Feint\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you score a critical strike with a melee attack, you can make a Bluff check to feint in combat against the same target as an immediate action.\n\n{b}Special:{/b}  You can apply the effects of only one critical feat to a given critical hit unless you possess Critical Mastery." compset="Feat" summary="When you score the perfect blow, you use it to set up a target for your next strike." uniqueness="useronce">
