  <thing id="fSkirt" name="Skirt" description="You can take advantage of a well-placed blow to skirt around your foe.\n\n{b}Prerequisite:{/b}: Dex 13, Dodge, Mobility.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} Whenever you score a critical hit with a melee attack, you can immediately make a 5-foot step as a free action, even if it&#146;s not your turn (such as when you make a critical hit as an attack of opportunity). This does not count against your total movement for the round, nor against the number of 5-foot steps you can take.\n\n{b}Special:{/b} You can apply the effects of only one critical feat to a given critical hit unless you possess Critical Mastery." compset="Feat" summary="You can take advantage of a well-placed\nblow to skirt around your foe." uniqueness="useronce">
