  <thing id="fSpellCrit" name="Spell Critical" description="Your critical hits with spells cause additional magic effects.\n\n{b}Prerequisite:{/b} Critical Focus, base attack bonus +9, caster level 9.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b}Select one 1st-level spell you know that affects a single target and is negated with a saving throw. When you score a critical hit with an attack for a spell, the target is also affected as if you had cast the selected spell upon it. The additional spell effect lasts for its normal duration or 1 minute, whichever is shorter.\n\n{b}Special:{/b}  You can apply the effects of only one critical feat to a given critical hit unless you possess Critical Mastery." compset="Feat" summary="Your critical hits with spells cause additional magic effects." uniqueness="useronce">
