  <thing id="fStupefy" name="Stupefy" description="Your attacks knock the smart right out of your foes.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you score a critical hit with an attack, you can forgo dealing extra damage to instead deal 1d4 Intelligence damage. Weapons with a critical multiplier greater than x2 deal +1 ability damage for every additional multiple (thus a Stupefy delivered with a greataxe deals 1d4+1 Intelligence damage).\n\n{b}Special:{/b}  You can apply the effects of only one critical feat to a given critical hit unless you possess Critical Mastery." compset="Feat" summary="Your attacks knock the smart right out of\nyour foes." uniqueness="useronce">
