  <thing id="fTakeaway" name="Takeaway" description="When you score a critical hit, you can grab a foe&#146;s gear away from it.\n\n{b}Prerequisite:{/b} Int 13, Combat Expertise, Improved Disarm, Improved Unarmed Strike.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you score a critical hit with an unarmed melee attack, you can also make a disarm maneuver on the same target as an immediate action. You gain a +4 bonus on your CMB check for this maneuver if your unarmed attack has greater than a x2 critical multiplier.\n\n{b}Special:{/b}  You can apply the effects of only one critical feat to a given critical hit unless you possess Critical Mastery." compset="Feat" summary="When you score a critical hit, you can grab a foe&#146;s gear away from it." uniqueness="useronce">
