  <thing id="fTrgetStrk" name="Targeted Strike" description="You are an expert at striking a foe&#146;s vulnerable spots.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you score a critical hit, you can draw one additional critical hit card.\n\n{b}Special:{/b} This feat requires the use of a deck of cards for determining the results of a critical hit, and these cards are available from the publishers of the roleplaying game this product supports." compset="Feat" summary="You are an expert at striking a foe&#146;s\nvulnerable spots." uniqueness="useronce">
