  <thing id="fFearBlow2" name="Fearsome Blow (CHA)" description="Your critical hits are frightening.\n\n{b}Prerequisite:{/b} Str 13 and Intimidating Prowess, or Cha 13 and Persuasive \n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you score a critical hit with a melee attack, you can make an Intimidate check to demoralize the same target as an immediate action. \n\n{b}Special:{/b} You can apply the effects of only one critical feat to a given critical hit unless you possess Critical Mastery." compset="Feat" summary="Your critical hits are frightening." uniqueness="useronce">
